<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title> Site Netfluxo</title>
        <style>
            #conteudo{
                height: 600px 100%;
                width: 1200px, 100%;
                background-color: black;
                background-size: 100%;

            }
            body{
                font-family: Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif;
                color: rgb(247, 243, 243);
                background-color: black;
                
            }
            .box{
                height: 600px;
                width: 640px ;
                display:flex;
                justify-content: center;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .imagem{
                background-image: url("./Assets/FluxoEMPI.jpg");
                height: 400px;
                width: 640px;
                display:flex;
                justify-content: flex-start;
                flex-direction: column-reverse;
                align-items: flex-start;

            }
            .botao{
                height: 25px;
                width: 30px;
                box-sizing: border-box;
                border-radius: 30px;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .play{
                font-size: medium;
                height: 30px;
                width: 110px;
                border-radius: 3px;
                color: black;
                background-color: white;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .bottom{
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                flex-direction: row;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                margin-left: 20px;
            
            }
            .informacoes{
                background-color: rgb(34, 33, 33);
                height: 200px;
                width: 640px;
                flex-direction: row;
            }
           
            .info{
                display: flex;
                justify-content: flex-start;
                flex-direction: row;
                align-items: flex-start;
                margin: 30px;
                margin-bottom: 40px;
            }
            .left{
                height: 250px;
                width: 380px;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: flex-start;
                align-items: flex-start;
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .right{
                height: 250px;
                width: 260px;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                margin-top: 80px;
            }
            .parte1{
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                flex-direction: row;
                align-items: center;
                margin-top: 40px;
                font-size: xx-small;
            }
            .parte2{
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: row;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: space-between;
            }
            h1{
                font-size: small;
            }
            h2{
                color: rgb(7, 144, 7);
                
            }
        
          
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div id = "conteudo">
            <div class="box imagem">
                <div class="bottom">
                    <button class="play">
                        <img src="./Assets/play.png" height="20x" width="40px"><img/>
                        Entrar
                    </button> 
                    <button class="botao">
                        <img src="./Assets/Mais.png" height="120%" width="200%"><img/>
                    </button>
                    <button class="botao">
                        <img src=" ./Assets/Curti.png" height="120%" width="200%"><img/>
                    </button>
                </div>    
                <img src="./Assets/LogoFluxo.png" height="200px" width="200px"><img/>
    
               
                <button class="botao esquerda">
                    <img src="./Assets/X.png" height="120%" width="200%"><img/>
               </button>
               <button class="botao esquerda">
                    <img src="./Assets/Mute.png" height="120%" width="200%"><img/>
               </button>
            </div>
             

            <div class="box informacoes">
                <div class="info left">
                    <div class="parte1">
                        <h2>100% relevante</h2>
                        <h3> 1993 </h3>
                        <img src="./Assets/livre.png" height="15px" width="15px"><img/>
                        <h3>  29 anos</h3>
                    </div>    
                    <div class="parte2">
                        <img src="./Assets/Top1.png" height="20px" width="20px"><img/>
                        <h1>Top 1 empresas júnior do Brasil</h1>
                    </div>
                    <p>O pame tem sido um processo desafior, porém igualmente enriquecedor, tenho aprendido muitas coisas novas, e saido da minha zona de conforto.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="info right">
                    <p>Elenco: Antônio Falcão, Victor Diniz, Karolinne Oliveira, e mais</p> 
                    <p>Gêneros: Engenharia, Química Industrial, Arquitetura e Urbanismo, e Comunição Visual</p>
            
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>